746200 ais, or has been, a Judge of a High Court; or
1945118 bhas, for- at least three years, held the office of a Member; or
225676 cis, or has been, a Member of the Indian Legal Service and has held, for at least three years, a post in Grade I of that Service; or
801626 dhas, for at least three years, held the post of a Secretary in the Law Department of a State Government.
